#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:585
msgid "If the command fails, `ptool.run` asks whether to retry the same command."
msgstr "Si el comando falla, `ptool.run` pregunta si debe reintentarse el mismo comando."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:585
msgid "If the current environment is not interactive (no TTY), an error is raised immediately instead of prompting for retry."
msgstr "Si el entorno actual no es interactivo (sin TTY), se produce un error de inmediato en lugar de pedir reintento."

